These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, disco, indie, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indonesian, indian, french
4 different pets are kept: pony, chinchilla, turtle, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, taxi, boat, van
 1. the canadian is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 3. the fan of classical is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is the indonesian##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
 6. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
 9. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the indian##3
10. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the fan of classical##7
11. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
12. the french is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
13. the person driving the van is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | disco | indie    | classical   |
| Nationality   | canadian | indian | indonesian | french |
| Pet           | chinchilla       | turtle   | hedgehog  | pony     |
| Transport     | airplane      | boat   | van    | taxi    |

