.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, avocado, cucumber, strawberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, epic, satire, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, malaysian, french, mexican
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, climbing, rugby, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
 2. the french is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 3. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
 4. the person who's sport is rugby is the brazilian##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the french##3
 6. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the person eating cucumber##5
 7. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the brazilian##7
 8. the person eating broccoli is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
10. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##5
11. the malaysian is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | broccoli   | cucumber       | strawberry    | avocado      |
| Movie-Genre   | action | scientific | epic         | satire   |
| Nationality   | mexican   | brazilian  | malaysian       | french |
| Sport         | surfing      | rugby  | badminton | climbing |

