.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, doctor, freelancer, analyst
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, romance, disaster, adventure
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, canadian
4 different pets are kept: pony, hamster, ferret, fish
 1. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
 2. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the architect and the person watching disaster movies##7
 3. the doctor is the brazilian##1
 4. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the analyst##3
 5. the american is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 6. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 7. the freelancer is not the person watching romance movies##6
 8. the person watching disaster movies is not the analyst##6
 9. the architect is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
10. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the doctor is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
12. the chinese is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Job           | analyst | architect | doctor | freelancer |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero        | adventure    | romance    | disaster    |
| Nationality   | american        | canadian   | brazilian   | chinese         |
| Pet           | hamster          | pony       | fish   | ferret           |

