.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, 7up, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, drawing, woodworking, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, writer, fisherman, coach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, disaster, thriller, documentary
 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 2. the coach is the person drinking milk##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 4. the person drinking water is the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person watching superhero movies##6
 6. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the fisherman##1
 8. the writer is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is writing##7
 9. the writer is the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the lawyer is not the person watching superhero movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Beverage      | milk | 7up       | iced-tea         | water       |
| Hobby         | writing     | reading    | woodworking   | drawing |
| Job           | coach   | writer | fisherman | lawyer     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary      | superhero          | disaster           | thriller |

