 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking water is the person driving the van##1
 9. the person driving the boat is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person driving the skateboard##7
10. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
11. the german is the person drinking water##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person eating kiwi##7
13. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

