There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, almond-milk, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, kiwi, asparagus, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, collecting, woodworking, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, snake, rat
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the snake##2
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is not the owner of the turtle##6
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person eating asparagus##5
 7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person eating watermelon##7
 8. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
 9. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
10. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating asparagus##1
12. the person eating asparagus is not the owner of the snake##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up   | lemonade     | almond-milk   | soy-milk |
| Food       | watermelon   | pomegranate | kiwi | asparagus    |
| Hobby      | woodworking | magic-tricks | gardening   | collecting  |
| Pet        | rat | frog     | snake   | turtle |

