.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, sprite, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, magic-tricks, puzzles, card-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, videographer, electrician, lawyer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, metal, trance, reggae
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 2. the fan of blues is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the photographer##2
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 5. the lawyer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of metal is not the electrician##6
 7. the electrician is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
 8. the fan of blues is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
 9. the lawyer is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
12. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
13. the electrician is on the left of the lawyer##1
14. the photographer is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
15. the videographer is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate      | mirinda        | juice          | sprite    |
| Hobby         | card-games | magic-tricks    | puzzles          | video-games |
| Job           | photographer  | videographer   | electrician | lawyer      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae       | blues | trance          | metal        |

