.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, card-games, sudoku, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, scientist, software-developer, firefighter
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, guinea-pig, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, tennis, handball
 1. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 2. the software-developer is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is the owner of the frog##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
 5. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 6. the owner of the cat is somewhere between the software-developer and the person who's hobby is photography##7
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
 8. the owner of the cat is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
10. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
12. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | skydiving      | sudoku     | card-games   | photography    |
| Job     | firefighter | software-developer   | scientist | freelancer |
| Pet     | frog        | guinea-pig     | cat  | lizard      |
| Sport   | badminton       | handball | basketball   | tennis    |

 